                        <interp inst="t18470510-name-1264" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WRIGHT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable M</hi> 63.) I saw the prisoner, on the 5th of April—I took charge of the two boxes of bottles—I found fifty-one bottles in each of the two bottom tiers, and forty-eight in the other—there were six more bottles than there ought to be.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
