                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> He brought these bottles back as if he had not sold them, when he had sold others instead of them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I borrowed to loans of 20<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. for him—I borrowed them for my master—I am answerable for it—here is the letter sent to me about it—he said he would do everything to serve me. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I am answerable for it, not him—I am to pay it back by instalments.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">COURT</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How came the man to borrow money for you? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I was short of money—it requires one person to borrow it, and another to be security.</p>
